    "description": "这里是我们的游戏DEMO<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2>《终末方舟》是一款卡牌构建游戏。它融合了《陷阵之志》和《怪物火车》的玩法，并带有策略战棋和肉鸽元素。玩家需要在毁灭后的世界建立管理局，召唤单位，使用法术，来抵御各种敌人的进攻，并扩大控制区域，重新建立秩序。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特的战斗体验</li></ul>上百张不同的卡牌，多维度的战斗机制，让你每次游戏都会有不同的体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>多种战斗策略</li></ul></h2>面对大量敌人，你可以正面对抗，也可以全力防御。面对强大首领，你可以卡位牵制，也可以取巧斩杀。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>献祭系统</li></ul>独特的献祭召唤，组合出强大的战斗单位<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842640/extras/87be5b31ce6beec4452ac8b739694522.poster.avif?t=1670810185\" width=502 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842640/extras/87be5b31ce6beec4452ac8b739694522.webm?t=1670810185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842640/extras/87be5b31ce6beec4452ac8b739694522.mp4?t=1670810185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842640/extras/a4b366886dc083245e334269c2780b3b.poster.avif?t=1670810185\" width=502 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842640/extras/a4b366886dc083245e334269c2780b3b.webm?t=1670810185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842640/extras/a4b366886dc083245e334269c2780b3b.mp4?t=1670810185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >qq群:769146009</h2>",
